object.text: Милый бариста Александр готовит прекрасный кофе ^^
Salmon with broccoli and rice is amazing!
Everything is just fantastic: food is fresh and menu is very complete. Service is fast. Design is just beautiful! Try grilled salmon with fresh vegs plate. Highly recommended!!!
